title: 3 Buffalo Wild Wings in Alabama, Mississippi included in $11 million sale
text:
Published By: Al.com: Huntsville - Today 
Three Buffalo Wild Wings restaurants in Alabama and Mississippi were part of a recent $11 million sale brokered by Colliers International....
